  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="KT66-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">paruvaṅ kaṇṭu aḻinta talaimakaḷait tōḻi “paruvam aṉṟu” eṉṟu vaṟpuṟīiyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">The confidante encouraging HER, who was desolate when
          seeing the season, [by the words] “that is not the season”.</p>
      </div>


      <div xml:id="KT66">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> maṭava maṉṟa taṭavunilaik koṉṟai</l>
          <l> kalpiṟaṅ kattañ ceṉṟōr kūṟiya</l>
          <l> paruvam vārā vaḷavai neritarak</l>
          <l> kompucēr koṭiyiṇa rūḻtta</l>
          <l> vampa māriyaik kāreṉa matittē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l>Foolish indeed [are] the broad-shaped Laburnum trees,</l>
          <l rend="indent">having taken the new showers for the rainy season</l>
          <l rend="indent">when trailing clusters joined to twigs have blown</l>
          <l rend="indent">so that they are crushed all the while the season has not come</l>
          <l rend="indent">that he named, who had gone the road glistening with stones.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
